Portland Bike Trails.description:
Portland has many miles of bicycle and pedestrian paths to help you increase your physical activity. This map is a useful guide for navigating SW stairways, bridges, trails and cut-throughs. Taking public transit is an easy way to increase the amount you walk too.

See https://www.portlandoregon.gov/transportation/article/321391 for more maps.
